<template>
<svg width="90" height="60" viewBox="0 0 90 60" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="empty-theme-river-svg">
<path class="river" d="M10,40 Q30,20 50,40 Q70,60 90,40" stroke="#4F8EF7" stroke-width="8" fill="none" />
<path class="river2" d="M10,50 Q30,30 50,50 Q70,70 90,50" stroke="#A0C4FF" stroke-width="6" fill="none" />
<path class="river3" d="M10,60 Q30,40 50,60 Q70,80 90,60" stroke="#FFB300" stroke-width="4" fill="none" />
</svg>
</template>
<script setup>

</script>
<style scoped>
.empty-theme-river-svg {
    display: block;
    margin: 0 auto;
    animation: floatX 3.2s ease-in-out infinite;
}
.river, .river2, .river3 {
    stroke-dasharray: 120;
    stroke-dashoffset: 120;
    animation: river-draw 1.5s cubic-bezier(.4,1.6,.6,1) forwards;
}
.river2 { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
.river3 { animation-delay: 0.6s; }
@keyframes river-draw {
    to { stroke-dashoffset: 0; }
}
@keyframes floatX {
    0% { transform: translateY(0) translateX(0); }
    25% { transform: translateY(-8px) translateX(4px); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-12px) translateX(-4px); }
    75% { transform: translateY(-8px) translateX(4px); }
    100% { transform: translateY(0) translateX(0); }
}
</style>
